{
  "id": "water-flowmap",
  "title": "水体渲染笔记：FlowMap 与法线扰动",
  "date": "2026-05-19",
  "summary": "简单整理 FlowMap 的原理、采样方式，以及如何用法线扰动模拟流动水面的质感。",
  "tags": ["HLSL", "Water", "FlowMap"],
  "content": [
    "## FlowMap 原理",
    "",
    "FlowMap 是一张存储了二维方向向量的贴图，`R/G` 通道映射到 `[-1, 1]` 的 X/Y 偏移值，用来引导贴图采样的方向。",
    "",
    "## 核心代码片段函数封装",
    "",
    "```hlsl",
    "half4 FlowMapNode(Texture2D mainTex, SamplerState sampler_mainTex, Texture2D flowMap, SamplerState sampler_flowMap, float2 mainUV, float tilling, float flowSpeed, float strength)",
    "{",
    "   half speed = _Time.x * flowSpeed;",
    "   half speed1 = frac(speed);",
    "   half speed2 = frac(speed + 0.5);",
    "",
    "   half4 flow = SAMPLE_TEXTURE2D(flowMap , sampler_flowMap , mainUV);",
    "   half2 flow_uv = - (flow.xy * 2 - 1);",
    "",
    "   half2 flow_uv1 = flow_uv * speed1 * strength;",
    "   half2 flow_uv2 = flow_uv * speed2 * strength;",
    "",
    "   flow_uv1 += (mainUV * tilling);",
    "   flow_uv2 += (mainUV * tilling);",
    "",
    "   half4 col = SAMPLE_TEXTURE2D(mainTex , sampler_mainTex , flow_uv1);",
    "   half4 col2 = SAMPLE_TEXTURE2D(mainTex , sampler_mainTex , flow_uv2);",
    "",
    "   float lerpValue = abs(speed1 * 2 - 1);",
    "   half4 finalCol = lerp(col, col2, lerpValue);",
    "",
    "   return finalCol;",
    "}",
    "```",
    "",
    "将采样的主纹理和FlowMap纹理都直接封装到了函数中，这样可以在片段着色器中直接调用该函数得到结果。",
    "",
    "## 视觉表现",
    "",
    "把法线贴入 PBR 流程后，再叠一层屏幕空间反射或 Cubemap，效果就足够撑起小溪、河流这类动态水面。",
    "",
